just want the meditation the vipassana and that's fine and most people these days anyway want to collect their own little spiritual portfolio you know a little bit of this a little bit of that and gather their own little direction in the spiritual life so these exercises may be of use to you in the long term but at least you know of them so we've done the body exercise about

