how to develop a good attitude towards the body but also how to undermine a certain wrong relationship to the body and this morning we did the metta which is about developing the heart we didn't do the forgiveness which I'll do tomorrow which is the other side of it and of course we did vipassana and part of that vipassana practice was also recognizing that you have to establish a sort of basic platform

