00:13:29,272 --> 00:13:51,567
simply because you can't prove it he doesn't want to get into arguments in those days it was seen one of the big entertainments was to turn up at a park on the full moon where all these ascetics would come and have a real old ding-dong battle as to who was right and who was wrong so he wouldn't enter into those sorts of discussions and

