strength of suffering that can happen when somebody you know goes when somebody's taken by surprise when somebody's in a state of shock I don't know whether you know the work of Elizabeth Kubler-Ross did you come across that it's a book called Death and Dying and she's one of the early investigators to what happens psychologically when you die she's she was a doctor and she spent her time with in hospices and

