00:19:11,986 --> 00:19:40,676
he's having discussions with kings and with local people and he'd obviously been to this place and he'd returned to find that actually they were following his teachings he says there was no well talk no gossip and so he really sits down and he tries to give them this teaching and it's called the direct path so the two way path is to develop this

