I never met her.

352
00:49:35,143 --> 00:49:36,184
Died quite a while ago now.

353
00:49:36,786 --> 00:49:39,048
And she said doing loving kindness meditation was a waste of time.

354
00:49:40,731 --> 00:49:44,496
That was very, that was peculiarly Zen, you know, Japanese.

355
00:49:45,958 --> 00:49:48,621
So, maybe that was nitty gritty.

356
00:49:49,101 --> 00:49:49,963
Stop wasting your time

357
00:49:50,197 --> 00:49:51,920
I always love his stuff.

358
00:50:02,739 --> 00:50:03,201
Very good.

359
00:50:03,260 --> 00:50:06,447
So I can only hope my words have been of some assistance.

360
00:50:06,467 --> 00:50:14,061
May you be liberated through your investigation of the body sooner rather than later.

